    "output": "```python\ndef fibonacci(n):\n    \"\"\"计算斐波那契数列的第 n 项\"\"\"\n    if n <= 0:\n        return 0\n    elif n == 1:\n        return 1\n    else:\n        a, b = 0, 1\n        for _ in range(2, n + 1):\n            a, b = b, a + b\n        return b\n\n\n# 示例用法\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    for i in range(10):\n        print(f\"F({i}) = {fibonacci(i)}\")\n```",
